<br>
Missing were some of my favorite hard earned gear...my Rune Etched Icewurm Fang, Iksar Battleshield, Shield of Falsehood, and my Large Sewing Kit (there may be other items, I am just not sure).  All of these items I earned through money raised hunting or by killing Sarnak after Sarnak to obtain it.  The Shield of Falsehood is a symbol of accomplishment.<br>
<br>
As soon as I noticed the anomoly I petitioned for assistance.  I was forced to wait 4 and a half hours for a guide to &quot;take my report&quot; and &quot;pass it along to a GM to investigate&quot;.  I waited most of the remainder of the evening into the late hours with no response.  I have waited hours today for a Guide to respond to my petition before giving up in disgust at the delay and the amount of time I have to invest to get a response.<br>
<br>
I am aware that there is no point in even doing anything with Sequi if he is to be reverted to an earlier save, thus I have been denied access to my favorite companion.  In short I am becoming very frustrated.  To the extreme.  Sitting around waiting for a Guide to answer a petition and then being passed on to a GM who never responds to you is about the most annoying thing I can imagine.  It is a huge waste of my RL time yet if I don't do anything I will be the only one who loses out.  Angry angry me.<br>
<br>
Just though I would let off a little steam.<br>
<br>
GRRRRRRRRRRRRRRRRRRRRRRRRRR ! ! ! ! !! ! !!  !<br>
